mainText:
I would like to leave my deepest condolences and prayers go to Steve' s family at this extremely sad time. I know from loosing a family member recently what they are going through. 

His legacy will live on with all that he has done and for what he did and what Apple has become.

I would like to thank him for all he has done as I have been a mac user from the original iMac days and wouldn't use anything else. &nbsp;&nbsp;
